# .clang-format
---
# Style: BasedOnStyle: LLVM with 4-space indentation and 100-column limit
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
IndentWidth: 4
TabWidth: 4
UseTab: Never
ColumnLimit: 100
BreakBeforeBraces: Stroustrup
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: All
AllowShortIfStatementsOnASingleLine: false
SpaceBeforeParens: ControlStatements
PointerAlignment: Left
SortIncludes: true
IncludeBlocks: Preserve
ReflowComments: true
Standard: Cpp17
